metadata.name: MK 2 Bianca
metadata.description: MK 2 better known as Bianca is second in comand for the Meta Arkade. BiancaÂ´s personality is very cold and stoic in comparison to the rest of her sisters. Her role on the "Meta Arkade" is to designate the missions to all of the M.K according to their skills, she makes sure everyone is fulfilling their roles; helping them to improve. Bianca is known to have the highest ratio of success on their missions.
